P 同v先有用"},{"pid":"7a6421d2bb0cfa5fb5685fd0b3733e54cc5c9995","tid":1859830,"uid":84668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T11:08:18.000Z","msg":"補多啲圖先<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/32Dsccc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F32Dsccc.png&h=cd4e98fa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KHNpeqG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKHNpeqG.png&h=1512d757&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0363974dc714593bcfcf4d256792d7fff4bb214d","tid":1859830,"uid":2110,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T11:08:50.000Z","msg":"有BFE 防到飛沬夠一般人用架啦, 人多/高危環境當然唔合適"},{"pid":"cad1b7bc4c1951461c7e3b37176391caca11131b","tid":1859830,"uid":326897,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T11:09:16.000Z","msg":"記住,記住,記住,<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">==結論==<br />\nPFE &gt; VFE &gt; BFE<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n1. BFE/PFE/VFE<br />\n<br />\n口罩喺推出市面前需要通過各種過濾測試，亦需要於包裝上清楚列明其效率。大部分口罩都會透過 Nelson Laboratory Standard 進行測試，而日本口罩包裝上最常見嘅 BFE、PFE 以及 VFE 就係呢個測試中用作標示不同大小微粒嘅過濾率測試結果。<br />\n<br />\n1. BFE= Bacteria Filtration Efficiency = 細菌阻隔率（樣本大小: 3&mu;m, 容許: 1-5&mu;m）<br />\n<br />\n結論： 得BFE冇用，因為唔夠細<br />\n<br />\n2. VFE = Virus Filtration Efficiency = 病毒阻隔率（樣本大小: 0.1-5&mu;m, 載體: phiX 174）<br />\n<br />\nNelson lab 嘅測試可以隔到0.027微米，呢個size防到SARS既病毒有突，但唔係全部口罩都做到<br />\n<br />\n3. PFE = Particle Filtration Efficiency = 顆粒阻隔率（樣本大小: 0.1&mu;m）<br />\n<br />\n結論：因為飛沫最細只係去到0.6&mu;m，所以夠用<br />\n<br />\nPS: 醫護用會上到呢個standard。如果你相信政府，佢係飛沫傳染而唔會空氣傳染既話"},{"pid":"debdff41be4117f57d833c9bdc13e8784afcf66d","tid":1859830,"uid":148253,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T11:09:31.000Z","msg":"vfe太高階好難搵，但最少要有埋pfe先用得"},{"pid":"6e41a925574b387312dbf8f1e5dc9bf0fde1a4a3","tid":1859830,"uid":302831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T11:09:40.000Z","msg":"唔貴都可以頂住先"},{"pid":"69fe3ee451371d95d824118c2be749455d74a1a2","tid":1859830,"uid":335969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a6421d2bb0cfa5fb5685fd0b3733e54cc5c9995","tid":1859830,"uid":84668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T11:08:18.000Z","msg":"補多啲圖先<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/32Dsccc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F32Dsccc.png&h=cd4e98fa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KHNpeqG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKHNpeqG.png&h=1512d757&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T11:09:55.000Z","msg":"越南好過mic啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c96a5ab468b361bdf46d787f3c8550fe2a80879f","tid":1859830,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T11:12:23.000Z","msg":"飛沬大小數據, 絕大部份都係3-6&mu;m, 都係果句, 高危環境唔合適。<br />\n<a href=\"https://health99.hpa.gov.tw/DOC/980914%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E4%BB%8B%E7%B4%B9(%E9%99%84%E4%BB%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhealth99.hpa.gov.tw%2FDOC%2F980914%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E4%25BB%258B%25E7%25B4%25B9%28%25E9%2599%2584%25E4%25BB%25B6&d=sSzAGq%2B8hAhXqg0aovu9KeBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=38415560\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://health99.hpa.gov.tw/DOC/980914%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E4%BB%8B%E7%B4%B9(%E9%99%84%E4%BB%B6</a>).pdf"},{"pid":"55a4a99ac9685ad326d790e2cef406cda4d6d871","tid":1859830,"uid":194588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4931b75497448e62b6dfd4ba2c601bdcab494b7","tid":1859830,"uid":84668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da31e44da0c68310a7cdd632dcf3ca3e14dd1435","tid":1859830,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T11:03:34.000Z","msg":"有無果幾個英文?<br />\n即係PFE, BFE 同V乜鬼"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T11:04:36.000Z","msg":"上面剩係寫BFE 99%咋<br />\n冇寫VFE <img 